INSERT INTO realtime.position (
                id,
                vehicle_id,
                original_id,
                stop_id,
                source,
                geom,
                data,
                recorded_at
            )
            SELECT
                unnest($1::uuid[]),
                unnest($2::text[]),
                unnest($3::text[]),
                unnest($4::text[]),
                unnest($5::source_enum[]),
                unnest($6::geometry[]),
                unnest($7::JSONB[]),
                unnest($8::timestamptz[])
